page.title: 07FOOTBALL PRACTICE
page.content: WHEN I GET HOME ON A WEDNESDAY FROM SCHOOL I GET CHANGED AND GO OUT AND PLAY WITH SIMON. THEN AT SEVEN OCLOCK WE GO TO THE GLEBLANDS AT THE END OF SHAKESPEARE AVE BEDFONT. WE CAN WEAR FOOTBALL BOOTS OR TRAINERS SHORTS OR A TRACKSUIT.FIRSTLY WE DO HEADERS AND PENALTY SHOTS, PRACTICE TAKEING CORNERS ETC.AT THE END WE HAVE MATCHES. MY FIRST MATCH AGAINST BEDFONT SWANS IS ON 20TH JULY A SATURDAY MORNING AT 10.30. IN THE FOOTBALL TEAM THERE 10 BOYS, I GET ON WELL WITH THE BOYS. I HAVE TO PAY 9 POUNDS FOR THE KIT AND I HAVE TO PAY 3 POUNDS FOR SUBS. I HOPE WE DO WELL THIS SEASON.
